title: Peckham's Finest
overview: Peckham's Finest follows a diverse and aspirational group of young people from the area living everyday life in this eclectic pocket of London.With the cameras capturing all aspects of their lives, from blossoming romances to doomed relationships, from new friendships to broken ties and new ventures to everyday dramas, we follow our unsung heroes as they attempt to make their way in the world, hoping to turn dreams into a reality.
